<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your StaffCraft Analysis is Ready!</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #2563eb); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 20px; }
    .result-box { background: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #2563eb); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .stats { display: flex; justify-content: space-around; margin: 30px 0; }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-number { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb; }
    .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Your Analysis is Complete!</h1>
      <p style="color: #e2e8f0; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Ultra Premium AI-powered strategic insights ready</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Great news! Your StaffCraft Ultra Premium analysis has been completed successfully. Our 6 specialized AI agents have conducted a comprehensive strategic analysis of your requirements.</p>

      <div class="result-box">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">📊 Key Results</h3>
        <p><strong>Recommended Approach:</strong> <%= @analysis.recommended_approach.humanize %></p>
        <p><strong>Confidence Level:</strong> <%= @analysis.confidence_level %>%</p>
        <p><strong>Analysis Depth:</strong> Ultra Premium (6 AI Agents)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number"><%= number_with_delimiter(@analysis.total_tokens) %></div>
          <div>Tokens Analyzed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">$<%= sprintf('%.3f', @analysis.total_cost) %></div>
          <div>Processing Cost</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number"><%= @analysis.processing_time_seconds %>s</div>
          <div>Processing Time</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Your analysis includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🎯 Comprehensive options analysis with ROI modeling</li>
        <li>🔧 Advanced technology research and tool recommendations</li>
        <li>📈 Market intelligence and competitive analysis</li>
        <li>🛠️ Detailed implementation strategy</li>
        <li>📊 Complete input evaluation and optimization suggestions</li>
        <li>🧠 Executive-level strategic synthesis</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= frontend_url %>/analysis/<%= @analysis.id %>" class="cta-button">
          View Your Complete Analysis →
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px;">
        This analysis was generated on <%= @analysis.completed_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %> and remains accessible in your dashboard.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2024 StaffCraft Ultra Premium | <a href="<%= frontend_url %>">Dashboard</a> | <a href="mailto:support@staffcraft.com">Support</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
